cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR, cs.MM 

This paper is primarily focused on image classification and the robustness of Saak transform against adversarial attacks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses strategies for feature extraction, representation, and classification, which are related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. The paper also deals with adversarial attacks, which are related to computer security, making cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) a possible category. Finally, the paper uses datasets and evaluates performance, which is related to multimedia, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category as well.
